items.title: Hot Wire: 10 men to pluck off fantasy waivers
items.summary: Regardless of your holes, the fantasy waiver wire has a plug or long-term fix to pick up today. Check the following 10 men -- all sitting in waivers in many leagues, and all ready to help you win.
